Package org.open_ortho.dcm4ceph.core

Class BBCephalogramSet

java.lang.Object
org.open_ortho.dcm4ceph.core.BBCephalogramSet
public class BBCephalogramSet extends Object
This class represents a set of lateral and frontal cephalograms.

The BBCephalogramSet represents a set cephs, as stored in the Bolton Brush Growth Study collection. The set is made of one lateral and one poster-anterior Cephalograms and one SBFiducialSet. These all have the same Study and Series numbers.

Author:
afm

  • Constructor Details

    • BBCephalogramSet

      public BBCephalogramSet(File ceph1File, File ceph2File, File fiducialFile)
      Construct a new set of cephalograms from files.

      This constructor will load the passed files, generate appropriate Cephalogram and SBFiducialSet objects and use them to populate this instance. It will load the configuration from the default file name, which is the same root as the image file, with .properties as extension.

      Parameters:
      ceph1File - Lateral or PA image file.
      ceph2File - PA or lateral image file.
      fiducialFile - Fiducial distance information

    • BBCephalogramSet

      public BBCephalogramSet(Cephalogram ceph1, Cephalogram ceph2, SBFiducialSet fiducials)
      Create a new set of cephalograms from objects.

      This constructor will populate the set of cephalograms from the passed objects. This means the caller has to do all the job, and take care of setting the appropriate reference making use of the SBFiducialSet.setReferencedImages(String[]) method.

      Parameters:
      ceph1 - Lateral or PA Cephalogram
      ceph2 - PA or lateral Cephalogram
      fiducials - The set of fiducials.

    • BBCephalogramSet

      public BBCephalogramSet(List argList)
      Construct a new set of cephalograms from files.

      Same as 

       BBCephalogramSet(new File((String) argList.get(0)), new File((String) argList
         .get(1)), new File((String) argList.get(2)));
